description: Isohyetal map of Trinidad showing 75 years of mean annual rainfall for the record period 1911-1985 (in mm). The data was collected, isohyetals constructed and subsequent map produced by the Water Resources Agency of the Water and Sewerage Authority (WASA) of Trinidad and Tobago.
